channel.title: Close please
channel.description:
[s]Yes. I know another remake! But this will not be a fail one! i plan on making this remake big! [size=12pt]And WILL NOT GIVE UP![/size]
First off i should say that the base i'm using is pi.
Yes i know pi.. known for it's good combat system but very crappy skills!
We will be re-writing most of the non-combat skills too make them better!
You can go to are site here: [url=http://engrid-reborn.netai.net/index.php]Temp Site[/url] to keep update with the server!
Now it's time for some pic's and a update log!
The red color code means the feature has not yet been started. The orange color code means the feature has been started and is under construction. The green color code means the feature has been finished.
[B]Update's[/B] *Mining 90% done added prospecting [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3z7P0z45yHY&feature=youtu.be]remake-mining - YouTube[/url] *Started working on varrock *Started on tut island! *377 cache & client loading
[img]http://i.imgur.com/2EJAV.gif[/img][b]Combat[/b] *Pvp fully complete *PvN fully complete *Equipment requirements
[img]http://i.imgur.com/HhYtx.gif[/img][b]Magic[/b] *Every modern spell *Every ancient spell *Alching
[img]http://i.imgur.com/C2xH2.gif[/img][b]Range[/b] *Bows&arrows *Can't shoot through walls
[img]http://i.imgur.com/t0SHW.gif[/img][b]Prayer[/b] *All bones bury-able *Every prayer working properly
[img]http://i.imgur.com/4Ou9K.gif[/img][b]Mining[/b] *Emptying and refilling rocks *Prospecting *All ores can be mined *Random chance of obtaining gems
[img]http://i.imgur.com/Bbq6R.gif[/img][b]Smithing[/b] *All bars can be made *All bars can be made into items
[img]http://i.imgur.com/HFOC2.gif[/img][b]Fishing[/b] *All fish can be caught *Correct item requirements *Moving fishing locations
[img]http://i.imgur.com/Xvfj1.gif[/img][b]Cooking[/b] *Meats *Flour collecting *Bread *Pies *Stews *Pizzas *Cakes *Wine *Potatoes *Diary
[img]http://i.imgur.com/QrNzk.gif[/img][b]Woodcutting[/b] *All trees cut-able *Stumps and regrowing trees
[img]http://i.imgur.com/0HOQK.gif[/img][b]Firemaking[/b] *All logs light able *Clipped
[youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3z7P0z45yHY&feature=youtu.be]remake-mining - YouTube[/youtube]
[img]http://i50.tinypic.com/fbgrib.png[/img]
[B][size=12pt]Will add more soon! And i will add pic's soon![/size][/B][/s]
